mething.<br><br>I realized the only connection I have to the people on this mssg board is that at one time I played a game that I now hate, and they may or may not be currently be playing it. So why am I here? Well, I thought that since I played this game for a while, I'd have some common interests with people that played on the same server as me.<br><br>All I can say is, if I met some of the people on these boards during my time playing, I would have quit EQ a lot earlier then I did.<br><br>So, I'm not going to hold this up any longer, I'm not going to hold anything back. If any of these sound like you or someone you know, chances are thats the target.<br><br>I'm sick of all you holier-the-thou posters that think because you stay civil and don't use any derogatory speech when you pick apart posts, and think this puts you on higher ground then the people your arguing with, it doesn't. <br><br>I detest you jackasses that act like they're really open-minded, but in truth, they're just another prick on the boards that has to accept everything and only has the balls to condemn something when they know they have people that have got their backs, because they fear being put on the spot if someone gets offended at them. <br><br>For the people that actually post things just so that people will agree with them, I hope that little rush gets you through life, because its obvious you don't have much more. <br><br>People that actually insult people with things like being shut-ins or having no life? You play eq, thats the pot calling the kettle black.<br><br>All you people that consider "thnx la~ drive thru" to be an actual insult, from a "talent in writing" sense, you would be Carrot-top's bitch.<br><br>For you people that respond only to what you want in a post while ignoring the rest, I hope you do that with the road, and ignore the oncoming cars.<br><br>People that cant spell worth shit or don't use punctuation, your flaw gets enough attention as it is.<br><br>For the hypocrites that say that insult people be accusing them of doing these things, then turn around and do that on the next thread, Don't worry, your not alone.<br><br>Finally, for the fuckers that are just waiting to find a post that could be considered contriversial so that they can tear it apart and show someone how their opinion is so wrong and make them feel bad for having the balls to actually post what they think and feel, do the decent people here a favor, and leave. You won't be missed.<br><br>I came to these boards a few months ago, trying to be humorous. It worked out ok, but over time, the more I freely expressed myself, the more I became the target of attacks. This became a vicious downward spiral of assaults and rebuttals, and, well, it's led to this. Over time the taint of competition and augment slowly augmented me. I have to leave, so I wont be a part of this negative cycle any longer.<br><br>To all my RL friends, my time is up here, but we really don't need this do we?<br><br>To the admins, epically Tarot, you do a good job of keeping this place in line. I respect that, because I would never have the patience to babysit so may people, let alone add intelligent replies to many of the topics. Heh, guess its one less person to watch over.<br><br>To anyone that actually enjoyed anything I ever posted, thanks for your support, I actually got a kick out of alot of that stuff as well.<br><br>I guess thats everything. Know before posting here, that after I post this, I won't be coming back. You can beat the dead horse all you want, it means nothing to me. Its too bad that it had to end this way, but it had to end eventually. So long.<br><br><i>"Let us depart. No matter how difficult it is... we must live." ---Nausicaa of the Valley of the Wind</i><br><br>Azuza Whistlingfist  <p><BR><img src="http://azuza.homestead.com/files/azuzasig.jpg"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#D5D4D5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span